title: Why Do You Want To Lose Weight
itunes:title: Why Do You Want To Lose Weight
description:
Today we talk about how important it is to know WHY you want to lose weight. And the best part? You can have LOTS of reasons.
 
In this podcast we teach you how to find the reasons that are meaningful to you, and we give you an amazing tool to use to find them and check their relevance and importance.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
